The paper deals with a multi-user MIMO system with eavesdroppers, which involves information theory (IT) and multiple antennas (MM). The concept of secrecy also suggests a potential connection to cryptography (CR). The paper also discusses power allocation, which is related to networked systems (NI) and signal processing (SI).
